@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

@userId = 2
@postId = 12

### =========================================
### POSTS - Criar post (aninhado no usuário)
### =========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Harry Potter 5",
  "content": "Bla1 bla2 bbblaa",
  "category": "imaginação",
  "tags": ["sonho"]
}

### =========================================
### GET - Listar todos
### =========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/posts



### =========================================
### DELETE - Deletar
### =========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/posts/{{postId}}


### =========================================
### PATCH - Atualizar (PUT - substitui o recurso inteiro)
### =========================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/posts/{{postId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Harry Potter 3 (editado)",
  "category": "imaginação",
  "tags": ["imaginacao", "magia"],
  "published": true
}

### =========================================
### GET - Buscar por id do post (aninhado no usuário)
### =========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/posts/{{postId}}





### =========================================
### POSTS - Buscar por termo (query param)
### =========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?term=typescript

### =========================================
### POSTS - Buscar por id
### =========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}



### =========================================
### POSTS - Casos de erro (pra testar a validação Zod)
### =========================================

### title vazio -> deve retornar 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "content": "Conteúdo válido",
  "category": "tecnologia",
  "tags": []
}

### id inexistente -> deve retornar 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/999999
